nodes.text: A clone trooper pilot served in the Battle of Muunilinst as leader of Gold Squadron. He was killed by enemy Nantex-class fighters forcing Gold Two to lead the squadron.

As the battle over Muunilinst began a huge number of Geonosian starfighters joined the battle, Gold Leader was killed while the rest of Gold Squadron was decimated. Afterward Gold Squadron was ordered to get out by Commander Skywalker.
